songs.title: Something boring to listen
songs.lyrics:
(Yeah, yeah, prr, brr, prr brr)

(yeah, yeah, yeah, prrrr)

(Brrr, Prrr)

I'm still waiting, for that person
I keep screaming, I do not like that version

Pushed, tired, the talk
Pushed, tired, the walk

Stop seeing me like that
Stop walking like far

Wait it up (Ouu)
Wait it up

Yeahh yeahhhh (yes, yes)

I'm still waiting, for that person
I keep screaming, I do not like that version

Pushed, tired, the block
Pushed, tired, the jock (yeah yeah yeah prr)
